          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>S-Corp Access to Crowdfunding Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to the taxation of S corporations, to exclude from the 100 shareholder limitation for such corporations individuals who acquired shares in an S corporation through: (1) small public offerings, or (2) one or more crowdfunding offerings. </p>]]></text>
